---
title: Garlic Baby Broccoli & Green Beans with Lemon, Mint & Crumbly Cheese | Serves 2
description: This abundant bowl of green goodness is sure to put the pep in your step! With lemon and chilli there's plenty of zest and a gentle kick of heat, while crumbly cheese adds a delicious creamy touch.
